:name:
Rigor

:coretxt:
Vampire posses mystical inhuman endurance.
Can be used to remove incoming vigor damage but only up to three.
Each tier gives example what vampire is able to ignore.

:cost:
Vigor

:req:
Has been burning while looking at the sun.

:1:
Able to soak hit from a sword.

:2:
Can take a hit from a car and walk it off.

:3:
Is able to ignore hitting ground in terminal velocity.


:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricStrength
